

To get the sample site running locally:

Clone or fork the repo.
cp config/database.yml.example config/database.yml
rake db:create:all
rake db:schema:load
cp config/spreedly_core.yml.example config/spreedly_core.yml
use curl to create a gateway on Spreedly Core
Remember the gateway token.
Adjust the config/spreedly_core.yml with the details of your gateway token.

rails server
signup for an account

